A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To fix the salary of the sheriff of Fulton County; to provide for related matters; to repeal
2 conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
3 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
4 SECTION 1.
5 Notwithstanding any other local Acts to the contrary, the sheriff of Fulton County shall be
6 paid an annual salary in an amount not to exceed $260,000.00, to be paid in equal
7 installments from the funds of Fulton County.
8 SECTION 2.
9 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
